dc_title_s: Transportation, Planimetric Feature Edges: Prince George's County, Maryland, 2014
dc_description_s: This dataset contains road, bridge and railroad centerlines and curbs within Prince George's County. Railroad centerlines, or Metro lines, which continue underground and pass into a tunnel are coded with a hidden railroad feature code. This data was captured for use in general mapping at a scale of 1:1200.
dc_creator_sm: The Maryland-National Capital Park & Planning Commission
